}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Per the FCC photos... *"48DNUA50.SGE" and "2013/08/05" is silkscreened on the bottom of the board. **The following is silkscreened on the antennas.. ***"48DNUA51.SGF" and "2013/08/16" (#1) ***"48DNUA52.SGE" and "2013/08/05" (#2) *This device is using QCA9375X-AL3D. *UART test pads are accessible on the bottom of the board. *The device is using (at least) a 00:0B:6B OUI.
